headline: Steel Dynamics Completes Acquisition of the Remaining 55% Ownership Interest in New Process Steel
summary: Steel Dynamics, Inc. (NASDAQ/GS: STLD) today announced its completion of the acquisition of the remaining 55% equity interest in New Process Steel, L.P. ("New Process Steel" or "New Process"). New Process Steel is a metals solutions and distribution supply-chain management company headquartered in Houston, Texas, with a focus toward growing its value-added manufacturing applications.
